<h1>Banff Trail Calgary Real Estate and Homes for Sale</h1>
<p>Banff Trail is a mature and well-established neighbourhood and offers its residents a mix of old-school and modern. The residents enjoy an active lifestyle. This is a young community, with more than half of the population falling between 20 and 35. It’s a convenient neighbourhood for young families, students, and working professionals. </p>

