        <div>
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Schools In or Near Banff Trail</h3>
            <p>Located a short drive away from the University of Calgary this community offers an unique opportunity for families with older children. Attending the U of C while living in Banff Trail means you save on housing expenses while your children earn their degree!</p>
            <p>School age children can choose between three elementary and two high schools in the neighbourhood. There are several private, public, and catholic assigned schools in the neighbouring communities.</p>
